Package: sysv-rc-softioc
Architecture: all
Depends: procserv (>= 2.6.0~), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: conserver-server, epics-dev
Description: SysV style init script for softiocs
 This init script provides a way to automatically start
 softIocs on system boot.  After system boot they
 can be controled with the procServ process server.
 .
 See /usr/share/doc/sysv-rc-softioc/README for
 setup instructions after installing this package.
